lines: gang gi zhabs sen yid 'ong nor bu'i rdul
bgrang yas 'chi med dbang po'i tshogs rnams kyi
gtsug rgyan dang 'grogs bu ram shing pa zhes
sa gsum 'gro ba'i bla ma de la 'dud
'phags mchog nye bar 'khor nas legs bzung ste
bstan pa'i rtsa ba so thar bslab pa'i gnas
gtso bor legs ston 'dul ba'i sde snod mchog
gsal mdzad rgya bod 'dul 'dzin rnams la 'dud
tshul khrims ldan zhing 'dul ba'i cho ga shes
nad pa snying brtse 'khor ni dag pa dang
chos dang zang zing phan 'dogs la brtson pa
dus su 'doms pa de dag bla mar bsngags
slob dpon la gus tshul khrims yongs dag dang
bsam gtan dang ni 'don pa la brtson pa
grims shing dul la bzod dang ldan pa ni
sdom brtson gnas pa'i chos ldan shes par bya
mi tshangs spyod dang rku ba dang
mi la gsad par mi bya ba
rdzun du smra dang bcas pa yi
chos bzhi 'dir ni gsungs pa yin
zhes bshad pa ltar bzhi las
khu ba 'dzin pa 'khrig tshig bsnyen bkur smyan
khang pa khang chen dang ni gzhi med dang
bag tsam dge 'dun dbyen dang de rjes phyogs
khyim sun 'byin dang bka' blo mi bde ba'o
khang chen las zhes bya ba ni
sbyin par bya bas chen po yin gyi
tshad che ba ni ma yin no
zhes gsungs pa dang 'gal zhes gsung
des na khang pa'i lhag ma la gzhi
dang po ni mtshams nang gcig yin pa dang
gnyis pa ni bstan pa skyon med pa'i tshe'o
gsum pa ni dge slong kha skong bar 'os pa
bzhi pa ni chos ma yin par lta ba'o
'chang ba 'bral ba 'jog pa dang
'khrur 'jug pa dang len pa dang
slong dang stod g.yogs smad g.yogs bcas
rin thang so sor bskur ba'o
srin bal 'ba' zhig cha gnyis dang
drug dang mtho gang lam dang ni
'khru ba dang ni gser dngul len
mngon tshan can dang nyo tshong ngo
lhung bzed gnyis dang tha ga gnyis
byin 'phrog ston zla tha chung dang
dgon pa dang ras chen dang
bsngos pa dang ni gsog 'jog go
rdzun skyon dge slong phra ma dang
skyo sngogs byed dang ston pa dang
'don dang gnas ngan len dang chos
bshes ngor byed dang khyad du gsod
sa bon 'phya ba bsgo ba dang
khri dang gding dang skrod pa dang
phyis gnon 'byung ba 'debs pa dang
rim pa gnyis su rtsig pa'o
ma bskos nyi ma nub pa dang
zas dang chos gos gnyis dag dang
don mthun gru dang dben pa gnyis
dge slong ma yis sbyor bcug pa'o
yang yang dang ni 'dug gnas gcig
phye dang bca' dang stob pa dang
'dus dang dus min gsog 'jog dang
kha nas mid dang gsod pa'o
phrogs dang 'gril dang reg pa dang
bsngos dang dge slong min gyur dang
dngos po gyur dang skye ba gyur
dor bas kyang ni byin len nyams
bde dang me dang 'dun pa dang
bsnyen par ma rdzogs chos dang smra
dge tshul kha dog bsgyur ba dang
rin po che dang tsha ba'i dus
mtshal dang de bzhin rgya skyegs btsod rnams dang
gur kum dag dang mthing shing li khri dang
rma shing le brgan rtsi rnams mi rung ste
brgyad po tshon chen yin pas bkag phyir ro
dud 'gro 'gyod pa sor mo dang
rtse dang lhan cig sngangs byed dang
sbed dang gdeng med gzhi med dang
skyes pa med par lam 'gro ba'o
rku dang nyi shu ma lon dang
rko dang mgron dang bslab pa dang
'thab dang mi smra 'gro ba dang
ma gus chang 'thung dus min pa'o
zas bcas skya rengs da gdod dang
khab ral dang ni khri rkang dang
gdal dang gding dang g.yan pa dang
ras chen bde gshegs chos gos so
grong dang khyim gzhan nyid dang ni
bslab pa rnams dang dgon pa ni
sangs rgyas phan pa gsung pa yis
so sor bshags par bya bar gsungs
pus mo'i gong du sleb pa'i ha cang brtsengs pa dang
long bu'i tshigs la reg pa'i ha cang 'jol ba dang
phyogs gcig sar glang po che'i sna ltar nar ba dang
lte ba'i gong du sham thabs kyi mgo ltebs pa dang
'og tu sbrul mgo'i gdengs ka ltar byas pa dang
rab byung gso sbyong gzhi dang ni
dgag dbye dbyar dang ko lpags dang
sman dang gos dang sra brkyang dang
kau sham+bI dang las kyi gzhi
dmar ser can dang gang zag dang
spo dang gso sbyong gzhag pa dang
gnas mal dang ni rtsod pa dang
dge 'dun dbyen rnams bsdus pa yin
chos kyi ming ni sdom pa'ang 'di
zhig gnas lam du shes par bya
lhag mthong lam ni de don rnams
rnam par dpyod par shes par bya
de nas rdung bar byed pa yang
shing de nyid las 'bad de bya
sor bcu gnyis kyi tshad dag la
zlum zhing rtse gnyis ne'u le mgo
bdag gis rgyu skar smin drug brjod
zla ba nya tshe zla rangs 'gyur
ston zla tha chung zhes bya bar
yongs su grags pa brjod pa yin
gro zhun can gyi tshes gcig ni
snga ma'i dbyar te gtso bo yin
de bzhin khrums stod zla ba yi
tshes gcig ces ni phyi mar grags
mchod pa'i don du'ang rol mo'i sgra dang ni
glu byos zhes ni mi brjod 'on kyang ni
lha dang lha min dbang pos zhabs rdul gtugs
sangs rgyas la ni mchod pa byos zhes brjod
rgyal ba'i lung gi bstan pa sde snod gsum
de phyir rtogs pa'i bstan pa'ang bslab pa gsum
sde snod gsum 'dzin bslab pa gsum spyod pa
de dang drang srong chen po'i rjes su zhugs
yon tan lo thog ma lus skyed pa'i gzhi
rnam dag tshul khrims zhing sa yal bor nas
sku gsum 'bras bu'i phun tshogs don gnyer ba
de dag chu 'dod smig rgyu'i rjes snyeg bzhin
gangs ri'i phreng bas yongs bskor 'dzin ma'i gzhi
bslab gsum 'od kyis cig car khyab mdzad pa
jo bo yab sras mdzad pa'i rjes zhugs nas
tshul khrims bslab pa'i nyams len gsal bar byas
de las dung dang zla 'od kun da ltar
dkar ba'i dge ba gang zhig bsags pa des
'gro ba kun kyang nye bar 'khor lta bur
rnam dag bslab pa'i gnas la spyod gyur cig
de las zab dang rgya che'i ting 'dzin dang
rlabs chen thabs dang zung du 'brel ba yi
shes rab kyis bsdus rgyal sras spyod pa'i gnas
myur du mthar phyin thams cad mkhyen thob shog
